cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.CE, cs.CV

The paper describes a solution to a competition soliciting implementations of cryptographic schemes for machine learning in the context of cancer research. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories related to cryptography (cs.CR), machine learning (cs.LG), distributed computing (cs.DC), computational biology (cs.CE), and computer vision (cs.CV). However, since the focus is on the implementation of cryptographic schemes for machine learning, cs.CR and cs.LG are the most likely sub-categories.
